content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.18 - Use of running lights during hours of darkness

State Regulations

All aircraft being taxied, towed, or otherwise moved at the
airport shall proceed with running lights and anticollision lights illuminated
during the time between official sunset and official sunrise. Notes
